 mn gẖyr mwtk knt mạ hạqdr lạ ạ̉sẖwfk wlạ llsmạ
 ạ̉wṣl
 3- lmạ bạkwn kẖạyf bạbky klạmk bysẖjʿ qlby
 wḥlạwtk btkẖlyny ạ̉qdr mạʿmlsẖ kẖṭyẗ btgẖryny</lyrics>
